<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/complete-fix.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="fees-hero-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Fee Structure</h1>
                    <p>Transparent and affordable education for all.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div
                        style="background: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <div style="padding: 20px; background: var(--primary-blue); color: white;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0; color: white;">Academic Session 2026-27</h3>
                        </div>
                        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                            <thead style="background: var(--bg-cream);">
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="padding: 15px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;">Grade /
                                        Class</th>
                                    <th style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;">Tuition
                                        Fee (Monthly)</th>
                                    <th style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;">Annual
                                        Charges</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Nursery - KG</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 800
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 2,000
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Class 1 - 5</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 1,000
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 3,500
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Class 6 - 8</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 1,200
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 4,000
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Class 9 - 10</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 1,500
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">₹ 5,000
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <p class="note"><em>Note: The above figures are illustrative and subject to change. Please collect
                            the official fee booklet from the school office for exact and detailed information.
                            Additional charges may be applicable for optional services like transport, special coaching,
                            and excursions.</em></p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="payment-methods-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Payment Methods & Policies</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Online Payment:</strong> Fees can be conveniently paid online through the school's
                            ERP portal or mobile app.</li>
                        <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> Direct bank transfer facility is available.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cheque/Demand Draft:</strong> Payments can be made via cheque or demand draft in
                            favor of "N.R.K. Public School".</li>
                        <li><strong>Installment Options:</strong> For tuition fees, parents may opt for quarterly or
                            half-yearly payment plans.</li>
                        <li><strong>Due Dates:</strong> Fees are typically due on the 10th of the first month of each
                            quarter (April, July, October, January).</li>
                        <li><strong>Late Fee:</strong> A late fee may be applicable for payments made after the due
                            date.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="scholarship-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Scholarship Opportunities</h2>
                    <p>N.R.K. Public School is committed to supporting meritorious and deserving students. We offer
                        limited scholarships based on academic performance and/or socio-economic need. Details regarding
                        scholarship applications and eligibility criteria can be obtained from the school administration
                        office.</p>
                    <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button secondary">Inquire About Scholarships</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="call-to-action">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Any Questions on Fees?</h2>
                    <p>Our administrative staff is available to clarify any doubts regarding the fee structure.</p>
                    <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button primary">Contact School Office</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>